{"tid":1632240,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭搞咁多野 最終目的都係想取消區選 但冇人記得Solomon講咩?","createTime":"2019-10-06T17:20:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T17:42:03.000Z","uid":59518,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d94257f0103f88c845e13472f7cabbeb1c26f853","tid":1632240,"uid":59518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:20:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SolomonYue/status/1177806093025570818\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSolomonYue%2Fstatus%2F1177806093025570818&d=QZYHYFPECKJw76TN47EEpj632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=054557d5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSolomonYue%2Fstatus%2F1177806093025570818&h=7eadb1a4\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SolomonYue/status/1177806093025570818</a><br />\n取消區選即一國一制，香港法直接攬炒<br />\n<br />\n本來有區選 冇區選 輸既都係政府 都係保皇<br />\n我地又幾時變左咁撐林鄭  幫佢分擔取消區選既責任?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aab9ac4a589a18aead715cc35f0661376a68d079","tid":1632240,"uid":59518,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:23:44.000Z","msg":"如果你話 DQ晒佢咪贏<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/是咁的-我將-18-區-dq-主任-名單交咗比美國國會/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%98%AF%E5%92%81%E7%9A%84-%E6%88%91%E5%B0%87-18-%E5%8D%80-dq-%E4%B8%BB%E4%BB%BB-%E5%90%8D%E5%96%AE%E4%BA%A4%E5%92%97%E6%AF%94%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%9C%8B%E6%9C%83%2F&d=QZYHYFPECKJw76TN47EEpj632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=39f98891\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%98%AF%E5%92%81%E7%9A%84-%E6%88%91%E5%B0%87-18-%E5%8D%80-dq-%E4%B8%BB%E4%BB%BB-%E5%90%8D%E5%96%AE%E4%BA%A4%E5%92%97%E6%AF%94%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%9C%8B%E6%9C%83%2F&h=1a57c641\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/是咁的-我將-18-區-dq-主任-名單交咗比美國國會/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>委員亦主動問到選舉 DQ 的情況</strong><br />\n美國國會一早睇住喇<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解 我地要唔跟美國既劇本 走去跟林鄭個節奏玩?"},{"pid":"e4bb1a7690ce70f3a1d4c5ffc4f717595fcb3ff2","tid":1632240,"uid":235374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:23:57.000Z","msg":"緊急法背後最痛既就係有無限想像 結合現在既社會狀況 都唔知會發生咩事...係我都換定美金...<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb913e97c1df239f196cb22312f4fb1b27efd476","tid":1632240,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:23:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對店舖:記住唔需要次次硬裝修</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.打電話、EMAIL、無限FAX</span></span></strong><br />\n想同職員談心又得，講咩都得，幫阿SIR叫下外賣又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總知JAM到佢線就得。有EMAIL既就SEND EMAIL查詢下，有FAX機既可以用下無限FAX大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2.MEMO紙</span></span></strong><br />\n有開門就入去叫杯水慢慢坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3.善用1823</span></span></strong><br />\n食完野集體食物中毒呀，消防設備唔合符規格呢D無理由唔投訴呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留意返打完1823之後，佢係要起限期內比返回覆你架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢招長玩長有，大家打之前要謹慎少少呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">4.蟲系魔法師</span></span></strong><br />\n知道好多巴絲打鐘意養蟲蟲，但係入店一定要小心唔好倒瀉D寶貝呀(特別起食肆)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對人(限影大頭相/沒有攻擊性/非主攻類):</span></strong></span><br />\n記住召喚神獸唔係唔得，必須記住係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">對家首先用武力/拎住武器先可以召喚</span></strong></span><br />\n但係對住非攻擊形對手都召喚既話觀感就唔係太好睇，仲比左機會對家有煲大<br />\n對住非攻擊形既我地可以幫佢<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">飛個靚髮</span></span></strong>或者<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">化下妝</span></span></strong>就夠，唔一定要下下爆哂缸先叫成功架<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">*要記住中年人著緊自己把頭髮仲多過條命</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejjnAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejjnAS</a>"},{"pid":"5564b87dcdafc6ba92b464fffd08ed77bf0a8fc4","tid":1632240,"uid":331469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:24:13.000Z","msg":"[公投] 黎緊幾日勇武定和理<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1632191\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1632191</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b0b5714f67521c30ecb6ffe5d35ac065021cbbe3","tid":1632240,"uid":218298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:25:02.000Z","msg":"「認真」各位手足 借東風啊！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1629930\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1629930</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n麻煩幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3169dc6e9a09f25f6dfabe4281ce633543d4fdd7","tid":1632240,"uid":275901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:26:05.000Z","msg":"見到出邊啲po都話<br />\n真係要停一停"},{"pid":"6f6f0d0afc5c76d953e357f7c393bc9ff72d04bb","tid":1632240,"uid":138092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-0